Usually a football field
or a soccer field,

46:45.306 --> 46:48.309
or sometimes even a public park,
if there's enough space.

46:49.143 --> 46:52.514
Each opponent will stand
on opposite ends of the field.

46:53.147 --> 46:56.083
An official will signal
for the officials on the field

46:56.116 --> 46:58.986
