48:17.331 --> 48:19.299
I still count five.

48:20.134 --> 48:22.336
There are six weapons.

48:22.369 --> 48:25.573
A properly trained human body
is a weapon.

48:27.609 --> 48:30.645
I would like for you to start
working out on your own time.

48:30.678 --> 48:33.113
This way, we can spend
an entire hour

48:33.147 --> 48:35.349
