and hand-to-hand combat.

48:35.683 --> 48:38.252
I'm sometimes unmotivated
to work out on my own.

48:38.285 --> 48:40.588
It's easier when there's
someone there pushing me.

48:41.221 --> 48:43.290
The key is finding
something that you enjoy.

48:43.323 --> 48:45.225
There are many activities
that you can do

48:45.259 --> 48:47.562
that are also a great workout
such as bike riding,

48:47.595 --> 48:50.097
rock climbing, dancing,
or even swimming.

48:50.665 --> 48:53.400
Oh, I almost forgot.
I'll get you that DVD.

50:24.391 --> 50:26.694
