a full-face helmet,

54:35.643 --> 54:38.613
but another vehicle
ran a red light.

54:38.813 --> 54:40.882
And struck her head-on.

54:40.915 --> 54:43.483
She was alive for a few minutes.

54:44.484 --> 54:46.521
Witnesses say she even admitted

54:46.554 --> 54:48.723
