54:54.929 --> 54:57.932
First, we need to open up
the chest cavity

54:57.965 --> 54:59.967
and inspect the vital organs.

55:01.501 --> 55:02.970
I'm cutting into the skin...

55:08.676 --> 55:12.013
pulling it back to allow access.

55:16.918 --> 55:19.020
There. Next...

55:20.855 --> 55:24.659
we cut the ribs
surrounding the chest plate.

55:35.703 --> 55:38.806
Then we cut away the cartilage

55:38.840 --> 55:41.075
revealing the heart and...

55:59.727 --> 56:02.897
Bang, bang, bang.
Ah, the gun jammed.

56:03.097 --> 56:05.833
The first two shots missed, but
the last one got me in my side.

56:05.867 --> 56:07.802
It missed my vital
organs, though.

56:16.010 --> 56:17.678
Boom!

56:17.712 --> 56:19.847
Nice thinking.
Destroying my weapons cache

56:19.881 --> 56:21.782
would have definitely
sealed my fate.

56:31.626 --> 56:32.793
Ah!

56:34.996 --> 56:37.832
- Stab.
- Ah! I'm less mobile now.

56:38.833 --> 56:40.635
Stab, stab.

56:40.668 --> 56:42.904
The first stab
punctures my liver.

56:42.937 --> 56:45.940
I will die from this wound,
but not immediately.

56:46.574 --> 56:48.142
It will be slow and painful.

56:48.175 --> 56:50.011
I'm taking you out
with me, though.

56:50.044 --> 56:52.046
Slice.

56:52.079 --> 56:53.948
I'm cut.

56:54.682 --> 56:56.817
I'm bleeding severely,
and, oh, no.

56:56.851 --> 56:58.753
The knife got knocked
out of my hand.

57:01.689 --> 57:04.759
- Ah, ah...
- I block the sword,

57:04.792 --> 57:07.028
and tie up your hands
with the garrotte.

57:08.095 --> 57:10.164
Not only did that
force me to lose my grip,

57:10.197 --> 57:13.134
but it's also slicing into
the radial artery of my wrist.

57:13.167 --> 57:14.602
Ah!

57:18.005 --> 57:21.709
Not only is this cutting off
the blood supply to my brain,

57:21.742 --> 57:24.578
but the wire is
slicing into my flesh.

57:26.080 --> 57:27.715
I'm dead.

57:31.152 --> 57:32.586
Good.

57:33.955 --> 57:35.690
You should have used the gun.

57:35.723 --> 57:37.992
Always use the gun
if it's an option.

57:38.893 --> 57:40.161
I know, I just...

57:40.194 --> 57:42.063
I find guns to be
boring and overused.

57:42.096 --> 57:44.031
I know what you mean,
but if it's the difference

57:44.065 --> 57:46.033
between life and death,
it's okay to be boring.

57:47.835 --> 57:49.637
Only a week to go,
but I would say

57:49.670 --> 57:53.207
