I had yesterday.

59:34.341 --> 59:35.976
<i>On what?</i>

59:36.343 --> 59:38.813
An outfit for the duel.

59:40.314 --> 59:41.882
<i>If you default on your payments,</i>

59:41.916 --> 59:43.784
<i>the court will
assign you a handicap.</i>

59:43.818 --> 59:45.395
<i>Such as having to duel with one
arm tied behind your back.</i>

59:45.419 --> 59:47.054
